{"id":269581,"link":"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/2012/12/奇闻录-惊心一瞬/","date":"2012-12-21T15:01:38Z","modified":"2012-12-21T15:01:38Z","title":"奇闻录 | 惊心一瞬","content":"<p><p>12月20日，一男子爬上佛山汽车站近三层楼高的天棚欲轻生。尽管期间男子不时与警方交谈，并吃下后者送来的食品，情绪始终平静。但三小时后，男子却突然从天棚纵身跳下。医生称，男子颅脑受伤、全身多处骨折，目前生命垂危。<span></span></p>\n<div><a rel=\"nofollow\" href=\"http://qiwen.lu/wp-content/uploads/50d3acc7d2d9c.jpg\"><img alt=\"\" src=\"http://qiwen.lu/wp-content/uploads/50d3acc7d2d9c.jpg\" width=\"500\" height=\"313\" /></a></p>\n<p>图为当日11点43分，男子纵身跃下雨棚，守候在下面的医护工作人员大惊失色，赶紧向男子坠落地点跑来。</p>\n</div>\n<p><div><a rel=\"nofollow\" href=\"http://qiwen.lu/wp-content/uploads/900x600_8J85LMCU00AP0001.jpg\"><img alt=\"\" src=\"http://qiwen.lu/wp-content/uploads/900x600_8J85LMCU00AP0001.jpg\" width=\"500\" height=\"317\" /></a></p>\n<p>11点整，男子站在雨棚边缘，警察蹲在旁边耐心劝阻。</p>\n</div>\n<div><a rel=\"nofollow\" href=\"http://qiwen.lu/wp-content/uploads/900x600_8J85LICL00AP0001.jpg\"><img alt=\"男子跳下后，医护人员赶紧上前急救。\" src=\"http://qiwen.lu/wp-content/uploads/900x600_8J85LICL00AP0001.jpg\" width=\"500\" /></a></p>\n<p>男子跳下后，医护人员赶紧上前急救。</p>\n</div>\n<p><p>更多图片请<a rel=\"nofollow\" href=\"http://news.163.com/photoview/00AP0001/30380.html#p=8J85LE5700AP0001&#038;from=photoPrev\">点击</a></p>\n<p> </p>\n<div><a rel=\"nofollow\" href=\"http://feeds.feedburner.com/~ff/qi-wen-lu?a=WmLwylTzvBQ:D6SPgKaGlQ0:yIl2AUoC8zA\"><img src=\"http://feeds.feedburner.com/~ff/qi-wen-lu?d=yIl2AUoC8zA\" border=\"0\" /></a> <a rel=\"nofollow\" href=\"http://feeds.feedburner.com/~ff/qi-wen-lu?a=WmLwylTzvBQ:D6SPgKaGlQ0:7Q72WNTAKBA\"><img src=\"http://feeds.feedburner.com/~ff/qi-wen-lu?d=7Q72WNTAKBA\" border=\"0\" /></a> <a rel=\"nofollow\" href=\"http://feeds.feedburner.com/~ff/qi-wen-lu?a=WmLwylTzvBQ:D6SPgKaGlQ0:F7zBnMyn0Lo\"><img src=\"http://feeds.feedburner.com/~ff/qi-wen-lu?i=WmLwylTzvBQ:D6SPgKaGlQ0:F7zBnMyn0Lo\" border=\"0\" /></a> <a rel=\"nofollow\" href=\"http://feeds.feedburner.com/~ff/qi-wen-lu?a=WmLwylTzvBQ:D6SPgKaGlQ0:V_sGLiPBpWU\"><img src=\"ht